-- MOVES-Jadwa names private equity and investment banking head
-- 
-- Thu Jun 26, 2014 11:02AM EDT
-- None



June 26 (Reuters) - Jadwa Investment named Saad Al-Saif as managing director and head of its private equity and investment banking business.

Al-Saif, who joined Jadwa in 2008, has 13 years of experience in private equity, investment banking, debt and equity capital markets, the Riyadh-based investment firm said.